Program: Discovery
Title: The first Americans
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrz5w
Last Broadcast Date: 09 May 2006
Aubrey Manning travels to Mexico in search of the first Americans. Although it is seen as the 'New World' the Americas were also a new world to older civilisations. The programme explores the work of archaeologists who have found evidence of life there over 40,000 years ago.